^ Wieczner, Jen (July 21, 2014). "New hedgie standoff: 'frenemies' Bill Ackman and Dan Loeb compete in charitable giving". Fortune. Retrieved 9 June 2016. 
^ "WEDDINGS; Karen Herskovitz, William Ackman". The New York Times. July 10, 1994. 
^ "Board of Directors". Human Rights Watch website. Retrieved 2015-07-28. 
^ "Staff and Board Members". Friends of the High Line website. Retrieved 2015-07-28. 
^ Smith, Emily (2016-12-22). "Billionaire investor Bill Ackman and wife in ‘big-money divorce’". Page Six. Retrieved 2016-12-31. 
^ "Bill Ackman reportedly splitting with wife in big-money divorce". CNBC. Retrieved 2017-02-24. 
