November (2)
      














About Me




Harbor Investment Conference


The Harbor Investment Conference, (HIC) is a forum for professional and non-professional investors to learn from top money managers. In addition to an exciting array of speakers, participants can expect engaging discussions and networking opportunities with the 200 + industry leaders and private investors expected to attend.

